         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶  ¶ bot Museum ¶ 14/7/72 ¶  ¶ I was much gratified, rev. and venerable friend, when I received by last mail your kind letter, ¶ Letter not found. ¶  ¶ and I feel deeply indebted, that you h...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">72.07.14a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Miles Berkeley</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Natural History<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Museum,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>London,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Botany Library, Berkeley correspondence, vol. 9.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">bot Museum</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">14/7/72</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I was much gratified, rev. and venerable friend, when I received by last mail your kind letter,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Letter not found</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and I feel deeply indebted, that you have spared some of your precious time in the elaboration and remissal of my fungi. I am however grieved to hear of you indisposition, but trust, as your constitution is so strong and good, that you will have shaken off your illness long before this entirely</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The occasions of seeing Aseroë in a living state or well preserved occur but very rarely and last of all to one, who is not likely to travel anymore extensively. But if such an occasion should arise, I will watch and examine the species closely.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your workings on the fungi of all parts of the globe are marvellous, and therewith you have stamped your illustrious name for ever on every square mile of the inhabitable world.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am proud of the possession of your autographic photogram for the series of those of illustrious correspondents.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        </seg>No image of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Berkeley<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has been identified at MEL, but see M to J. Haast, 29 July 1862 (in this edition as 62-07-29b) and notes thereto.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>My poor picture, made in 1865 (since which time I have not been in an atelier) follows herewith for your kind acceptance.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Phallus described by me<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The only<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Phallus</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>known to have been described by M, (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">P. vitellinus</seg>) was described in B70.12.03, p. 122.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was seen only in a<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">single</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>specimen by me, and is placed in Alcohol. I will send it to you in the next case, which is to go to Hooker. As it is an unique sample, it might be desirable to figure it. I will gladly avail myself of your permission to send you any more fungi, which may reach me, or which I may pick up myself</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Trusting that providence will grant you an Humboldtian age<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Humboldt died at<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the age of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>90.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>together with firm health I remain your regardful &amp; grateful<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have now also a Phallus of the section with a reticulate mantle from two widely separated localities, but only one specimen from each.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">One of these localities was the Richmond River</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">NSW;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">see M to E. Ramsay, 20 December 1872</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">See<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">also M to M. Berkeley, 12 February 1872;</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">M to G. Bentham,</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>15 July 1872</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">(</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">in this edition<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">as 72-07-15a</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">)</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Aseroë</p>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Phallus</p>
         </div>
